name: Quant II recitation
tagline: Materials for the Quant II recitations, Spring 2014
body:
### This is the Course Website for the recitation for Quant II.

The TA is Drew Dimmery (which is why this is on his github). Recitation meets at 11am on Fridays for one hour. His office hours are 1 to 2 and 4 to 5 on Tuesdays, in office 317 at 19 W. 4th St.

Retrieve the raw course materials from the github repository (I suggest you take the time to learn how to fork a repository). The presentations will be published below.

### Presentations

1. [2014-01-31 - Introduction to R](1-Intro-to-R.html) - [(handout)](1-Intro-to-R-handout.pdf)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
